# Lines & **Spans**

```css
.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
}

.example {
  grid-column: 1 / 4;
  grid-row: 2 / span 2;
}
```

<!-- slide -->

## Named **Areas**

```css
body {
  grid-template-areas: 'header header'
                       'nav main'
                       'nav footer';
}

h1 { grid-area: header; }
nav { grid-area: nav; }
main { grid-area: main; }
footer { grid-area: footer; }
```

<!-- slide -->

## **Single** Source of Truth

```scss
@media (max-width: 50em) {
  body {
    grid-template: 'header'
                   'nav'
                   'main'
                   'footer';
  }
}
```

